{"surah":75,"ayat":[{"surah":75,"ayah":1,"key":"75:1","arabic_uthmani":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ لَآ أُقْسِمُ بِيَوْمِ ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Nay, I swear by the Day of Resurrection;","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":2,"key":"75:2","arabic_uthmani":"وَلَآ أُقْسِمُ بِٱلنَّفْسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Nay, I swear by the accusing soul (that this Scripture is true).","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":3,"key":"75:3","arabic_uthmani":"أَيَحْسَبُ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجْمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Thinketh man that We shall not assemble his bones?","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":4,"key":"75:4","arabic_uthmani":"بَلَىٰ قَـٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّىَ بَنَانَهُۥ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Yea, verily. We are Able to restore his very fingers!","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":5,"key":"75:5","arabic_uthmani":"بَلْ يُرِيدُ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ لِيَفْجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ","arabic_simple":"","english":"But man would fain deny what is before him.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":6,"key":"75:6","arabic_uthmani":"يَسْـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوْمُ ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ","arabic_simple":"","english":"He asketh: When will be this Day of Resurrection?","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":7,"key":"75:7","arabic_uthmani":"فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلْبَصَرُ","arabic_simple":"","english":"But when sight is confounded","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":8,"key":"75:8","arabic_uthmani":"وَخَسَفَ ٱلْقَمَرُ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And the moon is eclipsed","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":9,"key":"75:9","arabic_uthmani":"وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمْسُ وَٱلْقَمَرُ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And sun and moon are united,","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":10,"key":"75:10","arabic_uthmani":"يَقُولُ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ يَوْمَئِذٍ أَيْنَ ٱلْمَفَرُّ","arabic_simple":"","english":"On that day man will cry: Whither to flee!","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":11,"key":"75:11","arabic_uthmani":"كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Alas! No refuge!","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":12,"key":"75:12","arabic_uthmani":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوْمَئِذٍ ٱلْمُسْتَقَرُّ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Unto thy Lord is the recourse that day.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":13,"key":"75:13","arabic_uthmani":"يُنَبَّؤُا۟ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ يَوْمَئِذٍۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ","arabic_simple":"","english":"On that day man is told the tale of that which he hath sent before and left behind.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":14,"key":"75:14","arabic_uthmani":"بَلِ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفْسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٌ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Oh, but man is a telling witness against himself,","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":15,"key":"75:15","arabic_uthmani":"وَلَوْ أَلْقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Although he tender his excuses.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":16,"key":"75:16","arabic_uthmani":"لَا تُحَرِّكْ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعْجَلَ بِهِۦٓ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Stir not thy tongue herewith to hasten it.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":17,"key":"75:17","arabic_uthmani":"إِنَّ عَلَيْنَا جَمْعَهُۥ وَقُرْءَانَهُۥ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Lo! upon Us (resteth) the putting together thereof and the reading thereof.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":18,"key":"75:18","arabic_uthmani":"فَإِذَا قَرَأْنَـٰهُ فَٱتَّبِعْ قُرْءَانَهُۥ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And when We read it, follow thou the reading;","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":19,"key":"75:19","arabic_uthmani":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيْنَا بَيَانَهُۥ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Then lo! upon Us (resteth) the explanation thereof.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":20,"key":"75:20","arabic_uthmani":"كَلَّا بَلْ تُحِبُّونَ ٱلْعَاجِلَةَ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Nay, but ye do love the fleeting Now","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":21,"key":"75:21","arabic_uthmani":"وَتَذَرُونَ ٱلْـَٔاخِرَةَ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And neglect the Hereafter.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":22,"key":"75:22","arabic_uthmani":"وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ نَّاضِرَةٌ","arabic_simple":"","english":"That day will faces be resplendent,","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":23,"key":"75:23","arabic_uthmani":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٌ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Looking toward their Lord;","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":24,"key":"75:24","arabic_uthmani":"وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍۭ بَاسِرَةٌ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And that day will other faces be despondent,","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":25,"key":"75:25","arabic_uthmani":"تَظُنُّ أَن يُفْعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٌ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Thou wilt know that some great disaster is about to fall on them.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":26,"key":"75:26","arabic_uthmani":"كَلَّآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلتَّرَاقِىَ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Nay, but when the life cometh up to the throat","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":27,"key":"75:27","arabic_uthmani":"وَقِيلَ مَنْ ۜ رَاقٍ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And men say: Where is the wizard (who can save him now)?","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":28,"key":"75:28","arabic_uthmani":"وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ ٱلْفِرَاقُ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And he knoweth that it is the parting;","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":29,"key":"75:29","arabic_uthmani":"وَٱلْتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And agony is heaped on agony;","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":30,"key":"75:30","arabic_uthmani":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوْمَئِذٍ ٱلْمَسَاقُ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Unto thy Lord that day will be the driving.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":31,"key":"75:31","arabic_uthmani":"فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ","arabic_simple":"","english":"For he neither trusted, nor prayed.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":32,"key":"75:32","arabic_uthmani":"وَلَـٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","arabic_simple":"","english":"But he denied and flouted.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":33,"key":"75:33","arabic_uthmani":"ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهْلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Then went he to his folk with glee.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":34,"key":"75:34","arabic_uthmani":"أَوْلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوْلَىٰ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Nearer unto thee and nearer,","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":35,"key":"75:35","arabic_uthmani":"ثُمَّ أَوْلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوْلَىٰٓ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Again nearer unto thee and nearer (is the doom).","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":36,"key":"75:36","arabic_uthmani":"أَيَحْسَبُ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ أَن يُتْرَكَ سُدًى","arabic_simple":"","english":"Thinketh man that he is to be left aimless?","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":37,"key":"75:37","arabic_uthmani":"أَلَمْ يَكُ نُطْفَةً مِّن مَّنِىٍّ يُمْنَىٰ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Was he not a drop of fluid which gushed forth?","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":38,"key":"75:38","arabic_uthmani":"ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةً فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Then he became a clot; then (Allah) shaped and fashioned","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":39,"key":"75:39","arabic_uthmani":"فَجَعَلَ مِنْهُ ٱلزَّوْجَيْنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلْأُنثَىٰٓ","arabic_simple":"","english":"And made of him a pair, the male and female.","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0},{"surah":75,"ayah":40,"key":"75:40","arabic_uthmani":"أَلَيْسَ ذَٰلِكَ بِقَـٰدِرٍ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحْـِۧىَ ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ","arabic_simple":"","english":"Is not He (Who doeth so) Able to bring the dead to life?","juz":29,"hizb":0,"ruku":0,"page":0}]}